title: We were killing some time,
post_data: We were killing some time, so the kids and I decided to take over the world. We built (with imaginary tools) a transporter, and put some silly straws in there to test it out. They all came back different shapes and different colors. Then we built a holodeck where we went back to 16th century Venice (my 12-year-old son's idea - I guess the history lessons are working?). We all did a lot of painting, but my son's character painted aliens and was branded a witch. Oops.
